title: BRIEF-Acteos H1 net income group share swings to loss of 469,000 euros
text:
BRIEF-Acteos H1 net income group share swings to loss of 469,000 euros Sept 14 
Sept 14 Acteos SA : 
* Reports H1 operating loss of 524,000 euros ($592,539) versus loss of 59,000 euros a year ago 
* H1 net loss group share is 469,000 euros versus profit of 67,000 euros a year ago Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8843 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
